<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8">在道教中得道成仙的人，他们是超凡脱俗并有神通变化超能力的长生不死的人。葛洪认为：</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8">仙人者，或飒身入云，无翅而飞：或驾龙乘云，上造天阶；或化为鸟兽，游浮青云；或潜行江海，翱翔名山；或食元气；或茹芝草；或出入人间而不识；或隐其身而莫之见。3</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8">蹈炎飙而不灼，蹑玄波而轻步，鼓翮清尘，风驷云轩，仰凌紫极，俯栖昆仑。4</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
