<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8">以富贵为不幸，以荣华为秽污，以厚玩为尘壤，以声誉为朝露。(同上)</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
